    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Aphidura jimoi sp. nov. Apterous viviparous female, holotype. 1. ANT (bar: 100 μm); 2. Anterior part of body (bar: 200 μm); 3. Posterior part of abdomen with SIPH and cauda (bar: 100 μm); 4. Habitus (bar: 500 μm)." ;
